title: Warhammer 40k - Dawn of War Collection
description:
This is a full package of Warhammer 40k - Dawn of War.

This includes:
Warhammer 40k - Dawn of War
Warhammer 40k - Dawn of War: Winter Assault
Warhammer 40k - Dawn of War: Dark Crusade

There are installation instructions with the game, and despite there being cracks on some of the disks, no cracking is necessary if you follow the installation instructions.

If you follow the installation instructions, you will need no cracks and all races will be unlocked for your multiplayer games in Dark Crusade.

Seeding will be very slow at first, because my upload isn\&#039;t the greatest. Therefore, I ask anyone that downloads this to please seed.

Thank you.
